content.description: Direct the Sommelier Network to airdrop 15 million SOMM tokens, from the 150MM Sommelier Community Pool, to Liquidity Providers of the Sommelier Pairings application, Uniswap Liquidity Providers as well as Osmosis Liquidity Providers based on their participation and liquidity participation levels up to October 31, 2021. \n Proposal details can be found at: https://community.sommelier.finance/t/sips-002-a-proposal-for-a-sommelier-token-airdrop-of-somm-to-select-liquidity-providers/272
content.title: [SIPS-002] A Proposal for a Sommelier Token Airdrop of SOMM to Select Liquidity Providers

content.description: In order to implement the will of the community to as defined SIP-001 and SIP-002, 14.6 million SOMM will be moved into a staging multisig. These values are derived from the computations provided by VolumeFi here: https://github.com/VolumeFi/somm_airdrop. This multisig will have two responsibilities. First, it will send 3.4 million somm to itself on osmosis for distribution to the addresses defined in the snapshot. Second, it will send 11.2 milion SOMM over the Somm gravity bridge to an merklemined distribution contract. Failure to execute these functions correctly will be considered a protocol failures and be resolved by a hardfork.
content.title: [SIP-004} Staging Tokens for Airdrop

content.description: Upgrades the Sommelier Chain to Sommelier V3\n This upgrade wipes the state of current gravity bridge to enable redeployment of the new Graivty Bridge contracts. The previous bridge will be abandoned. The allocation module to enabe Uniswap v3 cellars is deployed in this upgrade to enable demonstration of the Somm protocols data provider driven rebalancing. Please follow the instructions of the PeggjJV team for a successful upgrade.
content.title: CabernetFranc

content.description: The proposal increases the quorum of staked somm tokens required to vote. The upcoming airdrop enables permissionless proposals. As the Somm becomes more widely held and governance becomes more permissionless, it's imporant that the quorum increase to ensure widespread buy in from token holders for governance actions.
content.title: [SIP-005] Increase the governance quorum
